{"lastModified":1775132901116,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::8604ab50-f0d4-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nThe Azimut 55 Flybridge combines functionality with elegant, refined aesthetics. This extraordinary yacht’s layout was created with the idea of efficient space utilization in mind since she offers stunning interiors in 3 cabins accommodating up to 6 guests. From the cockpit seating through the salon, it’s hard to find a sharp corner anywhere making the boat stylish, but more importantly, safe.\n\nThe spacious flybridge, located at the top, provides an exclusive platform for outdoor entertaining, offering captivating panoramic views of the Adriatic Sea's beautiful scenery. The main deck, with its refined living spaces, bathed in natural light, creates a luxurious and  welcoming ambiance. The cabins, designed with meticulous attention to detail, offer exceptional comfort for guests, with a sumptuous owner's suite and well-appointed spaces.\n\nThe Azimut 55 Fly incorporates cutting-edge navigation technologies and first-class entertainment systems, ensuring a cruising experience that is as smooth as it is luxurious. She is thus the ideal choice for discerning guests seeking a distinctive experience aboard a luxury motor yacht while on holiday in Croatia and as her name reveals just Be Happy while on board.","blueprint":{"name":"BE HAPPY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::8604ab50-f0d4-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::5a63fe00-fdc2-11ef-9305-a56e2a469dfe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8604ab50-f0d4-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::5a6361c0-fdc2-11ef-9305-a56e2a469dfe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8604ab50-f0d4-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::5a653680-fdc2-11ef-9305-a56e2a469dfe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8604ab50-f0d4-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::5a4ec850-fdc2-11ef-9305-a56e2a469dfe/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8604ab50-f0